iSCSI Diagnostics & Error Reporting Extension

This document explains the architecture and implementation reasoning behind the new error reporting and diagnostics system added to the Python CLI metrics collector.

The goal of this feature is to evolve the CLI from a simple metrics collector into a practical infrastructure diagnostics tool capable of detecting:

iSCSI failures
storage issues
network problems
kernel-level I/O failures
initiator/target connectivity issues
